Comments: This is the count of items that have been received. This does not mean a pack quantity. For example if one box containing 20 devices has been received, and the code is for the box, then quantity is 1. If however, the code used to identify the product is the code of the device, then the quantity is 20.

Definition: Additional information about the delivery - this can be relevant history, any remarks by the patient or professional, etc.
